<s> The semantics of a P3P policy is that is applies to all data collection associated with a URI -- you cannot currently exclude data collected at  </s>
<s> that URI from your policy.  </s>
<s> If you only reference a particular element in your policy and do not reference the other elements at that policy, then your policy is wrong.  </s>
<s> This is especially problematic in the case of multiple policies applying to different elements on a page -- how would you explain that in the existing framework unless each element was submitted to a different action URI?  </s>
